# React Pages & Components

- Pages under `src/app/{feature}/page.tsx`; feature UI in `{feature}/components/`
- Shared UI in `src/app/components/` (Layout, Cards, Navbars, Modals, Buttons)
- Wrap feature pages with `{Feature}Layout` from `components/Layout/`

Typical *Today page:

```tsx
"use client";
import { useSession } from "next-auth/react";
import { useGrammarTodayStore } from "@/app/store/grammarTodayStore";
import GrammarTodayLayout from "../components/Layout/GrammarTodayLayout";
// LevelList + SentenceList inside layout
```

- SWR hooks for metadata/tabs; Zustand for filters, quiz lists, hide/show toggles
- Do not invent a new data layer — mirror `grammarToday` when adding modules
- Reference: `src/app/grammarToday/page.tsx`
